# Slice 3 — Add Purchase Cycle Selector

## Purpose

Stop the hidden weekly assumption in Simple Mode.

The current Simple Mode asks:

How many items do you expect to sell each week?

This is not enough for informal businesses because many do not work weekly.

---

## Placement

Place this question after:

What kind of business is this?

Before:

Where will you sell, and how much do you expect to sell?

